{"tid":441521,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解做豬咁慘，老馮要比人食","createTime":"2017-10-19T17:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T23:33:37.000Z","uid":103799,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f424acf5adc5267109829f10d7d1be1e93c79662","tid":441521,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:20:16.000Z","msg":"世界上最慘既動物應該都係豬，世世代代比人食，都食左幾千年，重要殺佢地手法層出不窮地殘忍。。。。<br />\n打杖死人慘，其實佢地咪重慘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90279a27bf73e5a2d323911ab4fbe678b75cafb","tid":441521,"uid":153933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:48:38.000Z","msg":"牛仲慘 又要耕田又要比人渣牛奶 仲要比人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d78cc4cbfdec85a90c437f00d320fd26511ce3","tid":441521,"uid":123711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:51:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df9d485c7bb4dbc62a2a8a9a571d8415ed9d7717","tid":441521,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:54:56.000Z","msg":"所有食用動物由出世到死之後都係一個悲劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ece0130de83d7ccd74004c229d66247c14e213","tid":441521,"uid":138834,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T23:33:37.000Z","msg":"出生嘅目的嚟<br />\n<br />\n我反而覺得豬好幸福<br />\n有飯食，有屋住，打從一開始就唔知咩係自由，自然就冇追求，痛苦嘅大概只有比人殺嘅瞬間<br />\n<br />\n如果我廿幾年人從未學懂自由，從未受過教育，從未開過眼界的話，一定會生存得更開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最慘唔係冇希望，而係知道有希望，但遙不可及"}]}